e":{"pid":"3a319e54e88edbc11ae34d2e596e2f78fc80bafc","tid":1958831,"uid":189179,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"e526a2fc4f0b818baffab43929a640fe7353d00f","tid":1958831,"uid":349889,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2020-04-05T03:35:07.000Z","msg":"背景：DSE 英文1左（知好廢 求指導<br />\n目標：想同d 英文level 4,5嘅人有咁上下程度<br />\n<br />\n如果自學的話：<br />\n每日背兩篇BBC新聞稿？<br />\n睇TED之後句句跟讀？<br />\n背單字唔建議？好多人話唔應該就咁背，要有前文後理先可以對個單詞有深刻印象"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-04-05T12:45:05.000Z","msg":"狂睇狂聽英文，ig fb全部follow英文，電視淨睇英文台，自己狂睇英文youtube,總之一有英文就睇，一見外國人就hey!nice to meet you!my name is.....,傾到佢嫌你煩，上reddit，9GAG,而不上lihkg,whatsapp用英文，所有野用英文"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-04-05T12:46:30.000Z","msg":"Av都英文，eg. Blonde, Busty, Milf 而不要 日本、本土自拍"},{"pid":"ccfbcea2a1e265ae43beada14422634ccc60b805","tid":1958831,"uid":196701,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-05T12:52:52.000Z","msg":"每日對鏡練習Sir，this way"},{"pid":"cb3dfd7b2415051a9963e38f331339731bc95569","tid":1958831,"uid":232442,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-05T12:58:08.000Z","msg":"如果你小學加中學練咗12年英文，都仲係覺得英文唔好，咁不如還原基本步，用返外國人自然嗰套：<span style=\"color: blue;\">先練聽同講</span>，自製語境。<br />\n<br />\n(0. 揀定係英式定美式。)<br />\n1. 搵個你自己有興趣嘅topic，搵下有冇youtuber用英文講，搵個岩feel嘅先好留低聽，聽晒之後，再播，呢個時候佢一開口你就開口，catch up講英文嘅節奏。<br />\n2. 聽英文歌，搵啲慢嘅情歌，佢唱一句你唱一句。<br />\n3. 跟返樓上咁多位巴打關於聽同講嘅建議，佢地已經推介得好好，但睇唔睇AV就自行決定 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n個人感覺：聽得明鬼佬講乜，同埋流利表達自己，繼續學習個動力係高過你睇得明一篇文。同埋流利唔係指你每次都搵到個準確嘅辭彙句子去表達，就算你native中文，我賭你都會攝啲廢字落去拖，等你個腦組織到自己想講乜，而英文都大把字係用嚟拖時間，睇youtube時可以順手學埋。"},{"pid":"c2e104c9b88b5a9599663d4363f8cdb8ceab7355","tid":1958831,"uid":137038,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-05T12:59:14.000Z","msg":"中學老師教，但其實都無點聽書，所以英文得4"},{"pid":"49bcdc5f1f7a571e2819edf0e7c5be552e692b2d","tid":1958831,"uid":23343,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-05T13:01:49.000Z","msg":"Lkf"},{"pid":"ff12a00062bb0c79cb6dec937a88e3b8396fcac0","tid":1958831,"uid":2896,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-05T13:02:46.000Z","msg":"去外國"},{"pid":"5ce8475e412f62b066e55980f3b4309b030c45d5","tid":1958831,"uid":164504,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-04-05T13:04:38.000Z","msg":"Dse英文二，自學英文入ugc英文系<br />\n好想幫番當初同我有一樣問題既人，巴打不妨留個tg, 因為三言兩語講唔晒<br />\n<br />\n至於其他見到呢個comment既人，google extensive reading,唔好睇字面解釋就當明左<br />\n真係用少少努力去學呢個language learning technique ，相信對你會有好大幫助"},{"pid":"c35b5d6362af64b8aefefbd1d96f84529dbc3ed7","tid":1958831,"uid":95358,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-05T13:05:38.000Z","msg":"如果鍾意打機嘅話，用英文打你鍾意嘅game 已經幫到好多"},{"pid":"bd6371dad95af798cbd109c69ba27a7d6a90945e","tid":1958831,"uid":91771,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-05T13:07:23.000Z","msg":"上Twitter/reddit 同五毛用英文搏火<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n當年會考隻A都係咁來<br />\n<br />\n不過嗰時係打online同上電腦forum/newsgroup同鬼佬吹水<br />\n<br />\n仲有聽英文歌<br />\n<br />\n總之搏命浸"},{"pid":"43d79027c9470aaf6b1e9ed8f6ae581e5ff01ce1","tid":1958831,"uid":325346,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-05T13:09:25.000Z","msg":"睇英文新聞viutv6<br />\n睇港台the pulse<br />\n睇南早<br />\n睇Young adult小說"},{"pid":"41332f08881d1a3ee518616e82bcd066a0765bac","tid":1958831,"uid":15501,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"449d5cc3e8969e30f2c80296c6e2f26456bb170d","tid":1958831,"uid":4574,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-04-05T06:02:25.000Z","msg":"youtube有得開script<br />\nnetflix 有雙字幕<br />\n<br />\n閱讀嚟講<br />\nBBC news<br />\n啲英文生字 文法係易入口啲<br />\nThe Economist 就難啲 但係學到嘢<br />\n<br />\n進階操練英文嘅話 <br />\n不如直接做UE卷<br />\n淨係reading<br />\n已經有齊mc, matching, 搵句子grammar 錯誤<br />\n<br />\nAL Listening 程度同BBC radio差唔多"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-04-05T13:40:51.000Z","msg":"Netflix點樣開到雙字幕"},{"pid":"d4986e8e6ea6a21a53350949cade23d495a02c20","tid":1958831,"uid":6604,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-05T13:43:54.000Z","msg":"Read read read"},{"pid":"e2b95465467941d4ca6ef56a657362e027f43888","tid":1958831,"uid":27196,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-04-05T13:45:31.000Z","msg":"首先，每個人有唔同程度嘅英文水準，唔同level就應該要有唔同嘅學習方法。<br />\n<br />\n作為second Language learner, 假設你係連 noun/ verb/ adjective/ adverb都未識得清楚咁分，係咁睇Netflix係冇用架。<br />\n<br />\n叫你睇breaking bad, black mirror 啲人講到鬼死咁快，你都學唔到啲咩，亦冇辦法感受到點解佢地會用啲咁嘅字會表達意思。<br />\n<br />\n所以，都係最基本，你係要熟左 英文 呢個語言嘅系統。<br />\n到底 點樣先可以 砌成一個sentence? <br />\n姐係 SVO<br />\n<br />\n然後再學sentence pattern<br />\nSimple sentence<br />\nCompound sentence<br />\nComplex sentence<br />\n<br />\n當你知道左個 句子框架，咩位置塞咩字，（姐係通常句子嘅beginning係noun）<br />\n咁你不斷吸收新嘅字，會學得快好多 。<br />\n<br />\n所以，上Youtube search d鬼佬教英文基本grammar，佢地讀得慢，用字易，你可以試試。"},{"pid":"8f1481f759a48964f27a7b23054c7caf2704bd11","tid":1958831,"uid":4574,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"41332f08881d1a3ee518616e82bcd066a0765bac","tid":1958831,"uid":15501,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"449d5cc3e8969e30f2c80296c6e2f26456bb170d","tid":1958831,"uid":4574,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-04-05T06:02:25.000Z","msg":"youtube有得開script<br />\nnetflix 有雙字幕<br />\n<br />\n閱讀嚟講<br />\nBBC news<br />\n啲英文生字 文法係易入口啲<br />\nThe Economist 就難啲 但係學到嘢<br />\n<br />\n進階操練英文嘅話 <br />\n不如直接做UE卷<br />\n淨係reading<br />\n已經有齊mc, matching, 搵句子grammar 錯誤<br />\n<br />\nAL Listening 程度同BBC radio差唔多"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-04-05T13:40:51.000Z","msg":"Netflix點樣開到雙字幕"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-04-05T13:46:34.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://chrome.google.com/webstore/detail/nflxmultisubs-netflix-mul/pjhnilfooknlkdonmjnleaomamfehkli\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fchrome.google.com%2Fwebstore%2Fdetail%2Fnflxmultisubs-netflix-mul%2Fpjhnilfooknlkdonmjnleaomamfehkli&d=635WHVioB6XLrmiJ2plDD06%2B9elrQwgXj79VqWXxFjk%3D&h=a0681e4a\" data-auto-link t